BT /F1 24 Tf 45.00 490.00 Td (2. Project Goal) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 440.00 Td (- Solve the Travelling Salesman Problem with a heuristic method.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 416.00 Td (- Parallelize the search with MPI on a multi-node cluster.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (- Measure correctness, input-size behavior, granularity, load balance, and speedup.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (- Keep the solver in C++; use Python only for visualization and plotting.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
