stream
BT /F1 24 Tf 45.00 490.00 Td (3. Travelling Salesman Problem) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 440.00 Td (- Input: N cities with 2D coordinates.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 416.00 Td (- Output: one closed tour visiting every city exactly once.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (- Objective: minimize total Euclidean route length.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (L\(T\) = _i=0^N-1 d\(t_i, t_\(i+1\) N\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 344.00 Td (TSP is NP-hard; exact brute force is only practical for very small N.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
