BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (- tsp_island.cpp: MPI island-model solver.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (- tsp_sequential.cpp: sequential baseline.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 344.00 Td (- test_*.cpp: unit tests for operators and local search.) Tj ET
endstream
