BT /F1 24 Tf 45.00 490.00 Td (6. Tour Representation) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 440.00 Td (- One individual is a permutation of city indices.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 416.00 Td (- Example for 6 cities: [3, 0, 5, 1, 4, 2].) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (- The last city connects back to the first city.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (- A valid tour must contain each index exactly once.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 344.00 Td (The fitness value is total tour length; smaller is better.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
