BT /F1 24 Tf 45.00 490.00 Td (7. Sequential GA Baseline) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 440.00 Td (- Generate an initial population of random tours.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 416.00 Td (- Evaluate all tour lengths.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (- Keep the best individual by elitism.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (- Select parents by tournament selection.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 344.00 Td (- Create children with order crossover.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 320.00 Td (- Apply swap and segment-reversal mutation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 296.00 Td (- Repeat for a fixed number of generations.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
