<< /Length 616 >>
stream
BT /F1 24 Tf 45.00 490.00 Td (8. Genetic Operators) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 440.00 Td (- Tournament selection: choose the best among k=5 sampled individuals.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 416.00 Td (- Order crossover: preserve a segment from one parent and fill the rest using the) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (order of another parent.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (- Mutation:) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 344.00 Td (- random city swap,) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 320.00 Td (- random segment reversal.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 296.00 Td (- Elitism: copy the best local tour into the next generation.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
