stream
BT /F1 24 Tf 45.00 490.00 Td (9. Local Search) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 440.00 Td (- Optional memetic step controlled by -twoopt.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 416.00 Td (- 2-opt removes edge crossings by reversing a segment.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (- Or-opt moves a short segment to a better insertion position.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (- Applied only periodically to the best local individual to limit cost.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
