BT /F1 24 Tf 45.00 490.00 Td (15. Parallel Algorithm) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 440.00 Td (Initialize MPI) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 416.00 Td (Read cities and build distance matrix on every rank) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (Create one random population per rank) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (for each generation:) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 344.00 Td (evolve local population) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 320.00 Td (optionally polish local best) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 296.00 Td (if generation is a sync point:) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 272.00 Td (local_best = best local tour) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 248.00 Td (global_best, owner = MPI_Allreduce\(MINLOC\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 224.00 Td (owner broadcasts global_best tour) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 200.00 Td (non-owner ranks inject partial migrants) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 176.00 Td (update convergence-stop state) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 152.00 Td (Gather final global best and write outputs) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 128.00 Td (Finalize MPI) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
