BT /F1 24 Tf 45.00 490.00 Td (16. Load Balancing) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 440.00 Td (- Default: same population size on every rank.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 416.00 Td (- This gives approximately equal compute work per rank.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (- The cluster run limits ranks per machine by the weakest machine.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (- Optional -auto-balance benchmarks local speed and gives faster ranks larger) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 344.00 Td (populations.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 320.00 Td (One GA population per process: coarse enough to avoid per-generation communication.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
