BT /F1 24 Tf 45.00 490.00 Td (25. Speedup Result and Conclusion) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 440.00 Td (- Speedup experiment uses 2N^*=4800 cities and fixed total population.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 416.00 Td (- Speedup improves up to 16 processes, then decreases.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 392.00 Td (- No-communication speedup is much higher than total speedup.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 368.00 Td (- The GA computation scales, but repeated collective communication dominates at high) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 344.00 Td (process counts.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 320.00 Td (- The island model is correct and balanced, but large process counts require larger) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 296.00 Td (problem sizes or less frequent synchronization.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 272.00 Td (Parallel level: task/exploratory. Mapping: 1D rank-to-island. Communication: blocking) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 60.00 248.00 Td (MPI collectives. Load balance: acceptable in the measured run.) Tj ET
endstream
